## Required
# Bot token from @BotFather
TG_TOKEN=123456:abcdef-...
# Comma-separated Telegram chat IDs allowed to interact (get yours from @userinfobot)
TG_ALLOW_CHAT_IDS=123456789

## Optional
# Working directory for `claude` subprocess. Default: $HOME
# CC_CWD=/home/luigi
# Override Claude Code model. Default: account default
# CC_MODEL=claude-opus-4-7
# Subprocess timeout (seconds). Default: 300
# CC_TIMEOUT=300
# State file (chat_id -> session_id). Default: ~/.cc-telegram-bot.state.json
# STATE_FILE=/var/lib/cc-telegram-bot/state.json
# Custom harness note injected as first prompt section (rules for Claude on how
# this process is managed). Default: generic note about self-restart on bot.py edit.
# BOT_HARNESS_NOTE="..."
